=========================================
USER IDENTIFICATION
=========================================

1. Student
   - Enters academic details
   - Provides attendance percentage
   - Provides previous semester marks
   - Requests mark prediction
   - Views predicted results

2. Admin
   - Manages student records
   - Manages dataset
   - Trains and updates ML model
   - Views prediction history
   - Generates reports

=========================================
MODULE IDENTIFICATION
=========================================

Module 1: User Authentication
--------------------------------
Functions:
- Register User
- Login User
- Logout User

Module 2: Student Data Entry
--------------------------------
Functions:
- Enter Student Information
- Update Student Details
- Validate Input Data

Module 3: Dataset Management
--------------------------------
Functions:
- Upload Dataset
- View Dataset
- Modify Dataset
- Delete Dataset

Module 4: Marks Prediction
--------------------------------
Functions:
- Load Trained Model
- Accept Input Parameters
- Predict Student Marks
- Display Prediction Result

Module 5: Prediction History
--------------------------------
Functions:
- Store Prediction Results
- View Previous Predictions
- Search Prediction Records

Module 6: Report Generation
--------------------------------
Functions:
- Generate Student Report
- Generate Prediction Report
- Export Reports (PDF/Excel)

=========================================
SYSTEM ACTORS
=========================================

Actor 1 : Student
Actor 2 : Admin

=========================================
INPUTS
=========================================

- Internal Marks
- Attendance Percentage
- Assignment Marks
- Previous Semester Marks
- Study Hours

=========================================
OUTPUTS
=========================================

- Predicted Final Marks
- Performance Category
  (Excellent / Good / Average / Poor)
